<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>관리자 대시보드</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/admin-dashboard.css" />
        <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200"
        />
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="admin-header">
                <h1 class="title">관리자 대시보드</h1>
                <a href="/" class="back-button">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span>
                    홈으로 돌아가기
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="admin-nav">
                <a href="/admin/user" class="nav-button">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">people</span>
                    사용자 관리
                </a>
                <a href="/admin/admin-list" class="nav-button">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined"
                        >admin_panel_settings</span
                    >
                    관리자 목록
                </a>
                <a href="/admin/logs" class="nav-button">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">monitor_heart</span>
                    로그 모니터링
                </a>
                <button
                    class="nav-button secondary"
                    onclick="showNotice('게시물 관리 기능은 준비 중입니다.')"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">article</span>
                    게시물 관리
                </button>
                <button
                    class="nav-button secondary"
                    onclick="showNotice('시스템 설정 기능은 준비 중입니다.')"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">settings</span>
                    시스템 설정
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="dashboard-grid">
                <div class="dashboard-card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">people</span>
                        <h3 class="card-title">총 사용자 수</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-value" id="total-users">로딩 중...</div>
                    <div class="card-description">등록된 전체 사용자</div>
                </div>

                <div class="dashboard-card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined"
                            >person_add</span
                        >
                        <h3 class="card-title">신규 가입자</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-value" id="new-users">로딩 중...</div>
                    <div class="card-description">오늘 가입한 사용자</div>
                </div>

                <div class="dashboard-card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">login</span>
                        <h3 class="card-title">활성 사용자</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-value" id="active-users">로딩 중...</div>
                    <div class="card-description">최근 7일 내 활동</div>
                </div>

                <div class="dashboard-card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">article</span>
                        <h3 class="card-title">총 게시물</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-value" id="total-posts">로딩 중...</div>
                    <div class="card-description">작성된 전체 게시물</div>
                </div>

                <div class="dashboard-card log-card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">timeline</span>
                        <h3 class="card-title">24시간 요청</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-value" id="total-requests">로딩 중...</div>
                    <div class="card-description">최근 24시간 API 요청</div>
                </div>

                <div class="dashboard-card log-card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined"
                            >check_circle</span
                        >
                        <h3 class="card-title">성공률</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-value" id="success-rate">로딩 중...</div>
                    <div class="card-description">최근 24시간 성공률</div>
                </div>

                <div class="dashboard-card log-card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">error</span>
                        <h3 class="card-title">실패 요청</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-value" id="failed-requests">
                        로딩 중...
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-description">최근 24시간 실패 요청</div>
                </div>

                <div class="dashboard-card log-card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">pending</span>
                        <h3 class="card-title">대기 중인 요청</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-value" id="pending-requests">
                        로딩 중...
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-description">현재 처리 중인 요청</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="recent-activity">
                <div class="activity-header">
                    <h3 class="card-title">최근 활동</h3>
                    <button
                        class="nav-button secondary"
                        style="padding: 0.5rem 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem"
                        onclick="loadRecentActivity()"
                    >
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">refresh</span>
                        새로고침
                    </button>
                </div>

                <ul class="activity-list" id="activity-list">
                    <li class="activity-item">
                        <div class="activity-icon">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined"
                                >hourglass_empty</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-content">
                            <div class="activity-text">
                                활동 내역을 불러오는 중...
                            </div>
                            <div class="activity-time">잠시만 기다려주세요</div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="log-monitoring">
                <div class="activity-header">
                    <h3 class="card-title">실시간 API 로그</h3>
                    <div class="log-controls">
                        <button
                            class="nav-button secondary"
                            onclick="toggleLogMonitoring()"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="material-symbols-outlined"
                                id="log-toggle-icon"
                                >play_arrow</span
                            >
                            <span id="log-toggle-text">시작</span>
                        </button>
                        <button
                            class="nav-button secondary"
                            style="padding: 0.5rem 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem"
                            onclick="clearLogs()"
                        >
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined"
                                >clear_all</span
                            >
                            지우기
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="log-container" id="log-container">
                    <div class="log-item placeholder">
                        <div class="log-icon">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">info</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="log-content">
                            <div class="log-text">
                                로그 모니터링을 시작하려면 '시작' 버튼을
                                클릭하세요.
                            </div>
                            <div class="log-time">대기 중</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="notice-container"></div>

        <script type="module" src="/admin-dashboard.mjs"></script>
    </body>
</html>
